<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/tips.css"></head><body><p><b>Analyze packages</b></p><p>Use the bundled <span class="control">Package Checker</span> plugin to make sure that your Maven and Gradle projects have no vulnerable dependencies. From the main menu, select <span class="control">Code | Analyze Code</span> and click <span class="control">Show Vulnerable Dependencies</span>.</p><p>The results of the analysis will be displayed in a separate tool window in which every found dependency will have a detailed explanation.</p><p class="image"><img src="images/package_checker.png" alt="Package Checker" style="border: 1px solid #55555;" /></p></body></html>